text: James Aldous (7 August 1882 - 1975) was a British diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre platform event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1882 births Category:1975 deaths Category:British male divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
